::Amperion::
    He was starting to get irritated with this fight no one was taking any 
damage.  He heard Gabriel get up but chose to ignore him until he got close.  
He continued slashing at Savior with his right sword but thrusted his left 
behind him and turned at the same time.  The needle pricked his side but his 
sword is still moving towards Gabriel.
